listing.description:
##Want to share specific lists with clients or stakeholders without adding them to your Trello board? 

This Orah Apps Power-Up is a Bonus Power-Up, therefore it will not count towards your board Power-Up limits. Give it a try now before the bonus is taken away!

Choose relevant lists and download them as a spreadsheet, PDF, or image for easy sharing. For more details on how to use Board Export see [this blog post](https://www.orahapps.com/blog/export-trello-boards-cards-and-more?utm_medium=referral&utm_source=trello_directory&utm_campaign=tpwup__marketplace-listing__all_2021-05-13)

**NEW FEATURE!** 
‚úÖ  - **Export Trello Comments, Activity log, Checklists and Advanced Checklists** including checklist due dates and members 

**Where it helps:** 
üìà - **Share a spreadsheet** containing your ‚ÄúDone‚Äù cards with clients
‚úâÔ∏è - **Email stakeholders a weekly report** by embedding an image of your upcoming ‚ÄúTo dos‚Äù
üóÑÔ∏è - **Maintain an archive** of all your lists with a PDF download
üñºÔ∏è - **Download an image / screenshot** of your board to print off or showcase in a presentation

![Board export types](https://orahapps-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/Export+Trello+to+Spreadsheet%2C+CSV%2C+Excel%2C+PDF%2C+Image%2C+.001.jpeg.001.jpeg)

##Export as:##

**To view an example Trello board click [here](http://bit.ly/3psC9to). And to view the sample export files click: [CSV](https://bit.ly/3xZtsLM), [Excel](https://bit.ly/3uFdC6T), [PDF](https://bit.ly/33wmRKD), [image](https://bit.ly/2Sz1vKs)**

- **Spreadsheet as CSV and Excel (xlsx)** - includes card ID, name, description, list name, members, labels, due date, URL, address (map), **attachments**, **all custom fields**, **Checklists and Advanced Checklists (including due dates and assigned members), Comments, Activity Logs**, Checklist Items Total, Checklist Items Completed, Votes, Last Activity Date, List ID, Board ID, Board Name.
- **PDF** - includes card name, description, list name, members, labels, due date, and **checklists and advanced checklists (including due dates and assigned members), comments**
- **Image as PNG** - includes card names and lists

![Board export demo](https://orahapps-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/BE+Directory+Listing+gif+-+April+2021.gif)

**Pricing:** 
- Annual billing: $24/year ($2/month) per user for unlimited Trello boards.
OR
- Monthly billing: $7.50/month per user for unlimited Trello boards.
_(You're purchasing a license key for **one user**, not an entire board's worth of users)_
_NB: All cards on your board can be exported with this Power-Up,  regardless of if you created/are assigned to a card_

Interested in trialling this Power-Up before you buy? Contact us [here](https://productsupport.adaptavist.com/servicedesk/customer/portal/51)

**Looking to purchase this Power-Up for 5+ users? [Get in touch with us](https://productsupport.adaptavist.com/servicedesk/customer/portal/51) for pricing details.**

**FREE Trello Tutorials**
*Looking to do even more with Trello? Learn Trello tips, tricks, and automation with our [free video tutorials](https://bit.ly/3zQzi3c)*

By using this Power-Up you agree to our [EULA](https://www.orahapps.com/eula), [Terms and Conditions](https://orahapps.com/terms), and [Privacy Policy.](https://www.orahapps.com/privacy)

Get in touch on our [support portal](https://productsupport.adaptavist.com/servicedesk/customer/portal/51)
